    "category": "Table",
    "text": "<table><thead><tr><th></th><th>Trường X</th><th>Trường Y</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>x&#772;</td><td>81,981</td><td>8275/102 ≈ 81,127</td></tr><tr><td>s<sup>2</sup></td><td>37,8</td><td>33,9</td></tr><tr><td>s</td><td>6,2</td><td>5,822</td></tr><tr><td>Q<sub>1</sub></td><td>313/4</td><td>925/12 ≈ 77,083</td></tr><tr><td>Q<sub>3</sub></td><td>3133/36</td><td>5325/62 ≈ 85,887</td></tr><tr><td>ΔQ</td><td>8,78</td><td>8,8037</td></tr></tbody></table>"
